title: 11/23: Mailbag! (Recorded Fri.) (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Taking a look at the latest injury news and spending some time on Jaylen Samuels (6:15) as we tell you why he could be great and why he could struggle this week. Then we give some DFS tips (10:50), read your Apple Podcast questions (13:46), bring the Fantasy Regulators on (28:15) and answer your emails (32:30) at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
 
To learn more about listener data and our privacy practices visit: https://www.audacyinc.com/privacy-policy
